                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Rome"
                    },
                    "body": "The class hierarchy seems curios by the way. We have {{RecordBatchStreamReader}} inheriting from {{RecordBatchReader}} but {{RecordBatchFileReader}} does not? Both should support nearly the same features for two slightly different formats, so I would expect both inherit from {{RecordBatchReader}}",
